These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, kale, pepper, radish
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish, turtle
4 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, whist, bridge
 1. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating radish is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person playing whist is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
 4. the person playing scrabble is not the person eating radish##6
 5. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
 6. the person playing snooker is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the person playing whist is not to the left of the person eating kale##8
 8. the person eating kale is not the person playing bridge##6
 9. the person eating apple is not the owner of the turtle##6
10. the person playing snooker is the owner of the turtle##1
11. the person eating kale is not to the right of the person playing whist##8
12. the person eating kale is in an even position##4
13. the person eating radish is not to the right of the person playing bridge##8
14. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the person playing whist##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | apple         | radish     | pepper     | kale         |
| Pet   | ferret | turtle    | goldfish     | chinchilla |
| Game   | scrabble       | snooker | bridge | whist       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, ivory, apricot, red
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, librarian, pilot
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, september, may, august
 1. the librarian is not to the right of the pilot##8
 2. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 4. the person who likes red is the freelancer##1
 5. the electrician is not the person who likes apricot##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 7. the person who likes red is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 9. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
10. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Color   | apricot          | black      | red      | ivory   |
| Job        | librarian     | electrician | freelancer | pilot      |
| Birthday      | august | september    | october  | may |

