.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, goldfish, turtle
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, d&b, techno
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, software-developer, chef, teacher
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the teacher##1
 2. the software-developer is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 4. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the teacher##5
 5. the musician is not the fan of blues##6
 6. the fan of blues is on the left of the teacher##1
 7. the fan of blues is not to the right of the fan of techno##8
 8. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 9. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
10. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the software-developer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Pet         | goldfish  | dog | turtle | chinchilla |
| Music-Genre   | country  | blues      | techno | d&b        |
| Job     | musician | chef       | teacher    | software-developer     |

