.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: billiardpy, rose, dahlia, daisy
4 different games are played: go, chess, backgammon, billiard
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, colombian, german, thai
 1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 2. the colombian is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
 3. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbilliardpy##5
 4. the person who growsbilliardpy is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growsrose is not to the right of the colombian##8
 6. the german is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8
 7. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
 8. the thai is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5
 9. the chinese is on the left of the german##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is the german##1
11. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Flower   | billiardpy   | daisy | rose    | dahlia |
| Game   | backgammon    | chess     | go   | billiard     |
| Nationality   | chinese | german   | colombian | thai    |

