.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, swisher, fonseca, pall-mall
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, sports, western
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, goldfish, fish, dog
 1. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
 2. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fonseca-smoker##5
 5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 6. the person watching western movies is not the fonseca-smoker##6
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is not the owner of the fish##6
 8. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the fish##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is not to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##8
10. the owner of the dog is the fonseca-smoker##1
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar         | fonseca       | tiparillo | swisher  | pall-mall    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports       | western    | scientific | fantasy    |
| Pet         | dog | rabbit   | fish   | goldfish |

