.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, guinea-pig, bird
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, documentary, horror
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, car, tram, motorbike
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person watching action movies##8
 2. the person watching horror movies is not the person driving the car##6
 3. the person driving the tram is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the person watching horror movies##7
 4. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
 5. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
 6. the person driving the tram is the person watching action movies##1
 7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 8. the person driving the motorbike is between the owner of the goat and the person driving the tram##2
 9. the person watching horror movies is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
11. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Pet          | lizard      | guinea-pig      | bird | goat |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action    | horror | crime     |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | tram | motorbike  | car |

