 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 2. the person who likes yellow is not the person watching spy movies##6
 3. the person who likes yellow is between the person who likes blue and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
 4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is not the person who likes brown##6
 8. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person who likes brown##8
 9. the person who likes brown is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
11. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person who likes brown##8
12. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
13. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
