3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
4. the owner of the frog is not to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##8
5. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
6. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
7. the person eating lime is the owner of the dog##1
8. the person eating lime is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the person who's hobby is singing##7
9. the person eating lime is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
