 1. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person who likes apricot##8
 2. the pakistani is somewhere between the person who likes lilac and the malaysian##7
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person who likes azure##8
 4. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the german is not to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##8
 7. the pakistani is on the left or right of the german##3
 8. the german is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
 9. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person who likes apricot##8
10. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
11. the german is not to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
12. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
13. the german is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##5
14. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
