 4. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 5. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 6. the person who likes white is the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person driving the ship##8
 8. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
 9. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
10. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
11. the person driving the quad-bike is not the person drinking iced-tea##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3     |      4      |
